OL,3,CMan bailed over businessman's 2004
OL,4,Cmurder
OL,6,FA man who was arrested on suspicion of
OL,7,Fmurdering a businessman in Leeds in
OL,8,F2004 has been released on bail.
OL,10,FThe 55-year-old was questioned after
OL,11,Fbeing arrested in Bradford on
OL,12,FWednesday over the murder of John
OL,13,FLuper.
OL,15,FHe has been bailed pending further
OL,16,Fenquiries.
OL,18,FMr Luper, who was 57, was attacked by
OL,19,Fmasked intruders at his home on
OL,20,FSandmoor Drive, in the Alwoodley area,
OL,21,Fon 16 February 2004.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/3
