OL,3,CMan bailed over businessman's 2004
OL,4,Cmurder
OL,6,FThe robbers tied up his wife, daughter
OL,7,Fand au pair before escaping with about
OL,8,F#100,000 in cash and valuables,
OL,9,Fincluding a rare Cartier watch.
OL,11,FMr Luper was found unconscious and
OL,12,Fdied at the scene from asphyxiation.
OL,14,FWest Yorkshire Police are continuing
OL,15,Fto appeal for anyone with information
OL,16,Fto contact the force via 101 or
OL,17,FCrimestoppers on 0800 555111.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/3
